name: The Hamilton Dining Table
description: This large rectangular dining table is sure to impress offering unparalleled luxury to any dining room. The table stands on a stylish and elegant cruciform base offering contemporary character and charisma. Finished in a high gloss or satin lacquer, available in any of Davidson's luxury finishes with the option of a smart brass or nickel base. Popular in our dark finishes, this table sits smartly within most decors.
